@startuml
title Kịch bản 1: Luồng xử lý Đồng bộ (Synchronous) - Gây ra vấn đề

actor User
participant "Web Server\n(200 Threads)" as WebServer
entity "Order Service" as OrderService
entity "Payment Service" as PaymentService
entity "Inventory Service" as InventoryService
entity "Notification Service" as NotificationService

skinparam sequence {
    LifeLineBorderColor #blue
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #A9DCDF
}

User -> WebServer : 1. Gửi request đặt hàng
activate WebServer #LightCoral

note right of WebServer
  Server chỉ có 200 threads.
  Request thứ 201 trở đi sẽ bị
  **timeout** hoặc **connection refused**.
end note

WebServer -> OrderService : 2. Giao cho 1 thread xử lý
activate OrderService

OrderService -> PaymentService : 3. Xử lý thanh toán
activate PaymentService
note right of PaymentService : Blocking Call (1s)
PaymentService --> OrderService : 4. Thanh toán OK
deactivate PaymentService

OrderService -> InventoryService : 5. Trừ kho
activate InventoryService
note right of InventoryService : Blocking Call (0.5s)
InventoryService --> OrderService : 6. Trừ kho OK
deactivate InventoryService

OrderService -> NotificationService : 7. Gửi Email/SMS
activate NotificationService
note right of NotificationService : Blocking Call (2s)
NotificationService --> OrderService : 8. Gửi mail OK
deactivate NotificationService

OrderService --> WebServer : 9. Xử lý hoàn tất
deactivate OrderService

WebServer --> User : 10. Phản hồi "Đặt hàng thành công"
deactivate WebServer

note over User, NotificationService
  Người dùng phải chờ tổng cộng **3.5 giây**
  và 1 thread của server bị chiếm giữ suốt thời gian đó.
end note

@enduml